---
title: Pan-Seared Tenderloin Steaks with Pan Sauce and Parsley-Butter Potatoes
description: Our tasty pan sauce pulls no punches, and this dish really lets it shine. For balance, we've paired it with warm roasted potatoes and hearty broccolini.
